Class MetaParam.MetaLoadedFromPersistence

java.lang.Object
org.infinispan.functional.MetaParam.MetaBoolean
org.infinispan.functional.MetaParam.MetaLoadedFromPersistence
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetaParam<Boolean>
Enclosing interface:
MetaParam<T>
@Experimental public static final class MetaParam.MetaLoadedFromPersistence extends MetaParam.MetaBoolean
Non-writable parameter telling if the entry was loaded from a persistence tier (NonBlockingStore) or not. This information may be available only to write commands due to implementation reasons.
Since:
8.0
